果</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你搵嘅原因係乜? 翻兜? 定係做SP?<br />\n後者的話, 我支持你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你真係支持我咁做？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我前題係你搵佢做SP, 而唔係諗住翻兜先叫你搵咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實分咗手就搵過第二個啦, 就算翻兜到個心態都唔同晒. <br />\n<br />\n做SP可以有聖母愛, 咁就唔同講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483db449101ae944d5d045f35080e39c94a90c38","tid":294694,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T09:59:44.000Z","msg":"過幾日我都諗住講 一句姐"},{"pid":"58fa97a07c31e9c43d30a7ebefcc89fd1be17219","tid":294694,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T10:03:12.000Z","msg":"犯賤"},{"pid":"69a3e38db47e9eb4d5968a2c881867242a53665a","tid":294694,"uid":101335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T10:04:15.000Z","msg":"你個ex生日關你撚事咩"},{"pid":"5f3e16f6e18db7ebb99f285bdf4d9489ea419b75","tid":294694,"uid":109159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T10:17:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我講左<br />\n但佢不讀不回我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時會諗點解要放到自己咁低<br />\n明明人地已經唔要自己<br />\n仲喺度關心人 講生日快樂做乜鳩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講得就預左架啦<br />\n犯賤</blockquote><br />\n我都覺<br />\n菊花俾人屌到爛<br />\n但都未醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁再犯下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢啲真係玩到冇癮/有第二個先會放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係一直冇第二個先未放棄<br />\n但其實已經冇乜癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為左忘記佢而搵過第二個又等如搵水泡<br 